# 17. Data Retention Policy

Despite not being a requirement within HIPAA, Ceresti understands and appreciates the importance of health data retention.  Ceresti has created and implemented the following policy to support data retention laws.

## 17.1 State Medical Record Laws

* [Listing of state requirements for medical record retention](http://www.healthit.gov/sites/default/files/appa7-1.pdf)

## 17.2 Data Retention Policy

* Current Ceresti Customers have data stored by Ceresti as a part of the Ceresti Service.
* Once a Customer ceases to be a Customer, the data collected by Ceresti will be retained for the period of at least one year.
